OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool mindfulness lessons 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdon't work for teenagers   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Giving teenagers mindfulness lessons at
OL,6, school to boost wellbeing is largely a 
OL,7, waste of time, a major UK study has    
OL,8, found.                                 
OL,10,FThe technique, which encourages people 
OL,11,Fto meditate and live in the moment, was
OL,12,Fno better than what schools were       
OL,13,Falready doing for mental health.       
OL,15,FMany pupils were not that interested in
OL,16,Fusing the method, calling it "boring". 
OL,18,FHundreds of teachers and thousands of  
OL,19,Fpupils at 85 different secondary       
OL,20,Fschools took part in the experiment.   
